<h3>SHIPPING TIMES AND COSTS</h3>

<p>Orders placed on the {{ company_title }} On-line Store will be processed, prepared and delivered to the courier within 24/72 hours from the Order Confirmation, from Monday to Friday.</p>

<p>Shipment and delivery of orders may be delayed when placed during sale periods or during the following holidays: 1 January,&nbsp; 6 January, Easter and Easter Monday, 25 April, 1 May, 2 June, 15 August, 1 November, 8 December, 25 December, 26 December.</p>

<p>All orders are processed automatically and we are unable to modify the shipping and delivery times.</p>

<p>STANDARD shipments in Italy will take place approx. in 1- 3 working days following shipment from our warehouse in Bologna (delivery times to the islands are approx. 3-4 working days).</p>

<p>Delivery times to European countries are 3-5 working days, for Cyprus and Malta 8-10 days and Russia approximately 15 days.</p>

<p>Shipping costs may vary from country to country.</p>


